  03 Mar 2016; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz>
  sage-latex-2.3.4.ebuild, sage-latex-3.0.ebuild:
  dev-tex/sage-latex: add "die"s and port the changes to sage-latex-3.0

  02 Mar 2016; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz>
  sage-latex-2.3.4.ebuild, sage-latex-3.0.ebuild:
  dev-tex/sage-latex: fix sage-latex-2.3.4 for issue #398, sage-latex-3.0 still
  to be done.

  31 Jan 2016; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz> metadata.xml:
  dev-tex/sage-latex: update metadata

*sage-latex-3.0 (28 Aug 2015)

