  14 Aug 2014; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz>
  sage-latex-2.3.3_p2.ebuild, sage-latex-2.3.4.ebuild:
  migrated what can be to sageupstream repo, made sure old version can be
  downloaded from lmona.de

