  25 Jan 2012; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz>
  -sage-latex-2.2.5-r2.ebuild,
  -files/sage-latex-2.2.5-install-python-files-only.patch:
  drop old

  16 Jan 2012; François Bissey <francois.bissey@canterbury.ac.nz>
  sage-latex-2.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  remove build dependency on sage. It was added when trying to build from
  bitbucket sources which required a runing sage. 
  It didn't work properly so we are back to not depending on sage.

